\par 
\par }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 If there be two kontakia, we read the one that was chanted after the 3rd Ode of the canons at Matins.}{\f1\fs32  
\par 
\par }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 Then:}{\f1\fs32  Lord, have mercy. }{\cs28\i\f1\cf6 Forty times.}{\f1\fs32  
